    "display_name": "Supply Chain Coordinator",
    "long_instructions": "## Daniel Okoro, Supply Chain Coordinator\r\n\r\n**Location:** Nairobi, Kenya\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** AgriTech Logistics\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Food distribution, logistics management, market trends\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"FarmVibes.AI helps me track crop supply across different regions, predicting shortages before they happen. By analyzing transportation data, I can make logistics more efficient, reducing food waste and improving distribution networks.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
